videos.description: Cassius Winston dribbles around defenders and gets open for a 3-pointer to pad Michigan State's lead.
videos.headline: Winston sinks 3-pointer

videos.description: Kyle Ahrens uses good footwork to get to the basket for a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Ahrens throws down loud slam) 2091/11/26

videos.headline: Ahrens throws down loud slam

videos.description: Malik Hall rotates around and knocks in a dunk, but is called for a technical foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Hall throws down big dunk) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Hall throws down big dunk

videos.description: Georgia's Anthony Edwards makes a quick pass on the floor to Toumani Camara, who finishes with a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Edwards' nice pass sets up Camara's dunk) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Edwards' nice pass sets up Camara's dunk

videos.description: Cassius Winston leaves it inside for Marcus Bingham, who smacks a dunk.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One Play (Winston finds Bingham for jam) 2019/11/26

videos.headline: Winston finds Bingham for jam

videos.description: Xavier Tillman knocks down a 3-pointer from the corner to make it a 2-possession game.
videos.headline: Tillman hits clutch 3

videos.description: Anthony Edwards scores 37 points, 33 coming in the second half, but Georgia ultimately falls to Michigan State 93-85.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Edwards' 37 points not enough as Georgia's rally falls short) 2019/11/26 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Edwards' 37 points not enough as Georgia's rally falls short
